{"tid":706453,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【球迷票選】近半數要求將基迪亞踢出正選","createTime":"2018-06-18T01:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T02:56:32.000Z","uid":30040,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1cab2caa514cfb2b10e629df976a07cbe4ef100f","tid":706453,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:54:57.000Z","msg":"　　根據《阿斯報》調查，在受訪的將近4萬人中，有一半支持目前的西班牙二號門將阿列沙巴拿加頂替迪基亞正選。<br />\n<br />\n　　《阿斯報》在昨天賽後對「門將位置誰該正選」這個問題進行調查，有39,917人參加調查，其中只有23歲的畢爾包門將艾利沙巴拿加獲得多達19,865的投票，達到49.77%。　<br />\n<br />\n　　作為正選門將的迪基亞只獲得15,332票，即是38.41%，老門將連拿獲得4,720票，即是11.82%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/06/17/b/b0c82824c5b2cf0a6ce45e7c71c7cfc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2Fb%2Fb0c82824c5b2cf0a6ce45e7c71c7cfc5.jpg&h=0574711c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a936de175f2ab24c333fc3ef1151c58efc4aaa4","tid":706453,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:59:23.000Z","msg":"唔好搞後生仔啦，<br />\n輸左由得ddg咩晒鑊咪得囉"},{"pid":"175e362a8d225dbdda2889cca7da3918d5997f57","tid":706453,"uid":21028,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:59:41.000Z","msg":"球迷就係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a42d0cbc7c11de26fe331b588203d89cd4121e","tid":706453,"uid":30454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:00:56.000Z","msg":"屌你邊撚個基迪亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db47199f3b76dddf5bb78abebc4ba046de68a5e","tid":706453,"uid":45408,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"咩topic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入嚟之前仲諗係迪基亞定基迪拉"},{"pid":"38ff6acc111e8ca429f83ba251a07c5c1bf47632","ti